      "sc:description": "A pipeline for prediction of Metagenome and whole-genome opeRons.\n\nMetaRon (Metagenomic opeRon prediction pipeline) is a computational workflow for the prediction of operons from metagenomic data. The pipeline predicts metagenomic operons without any any functional or experimental data. It comes with options to process the metagenomic data starting from filtered raw reads, which includes: assembly into scaffolds via IDBA, data manipulation, gene prediction via prodigal and lastly operon prediction based on gene's co-directionality, intergenic distance (IGD) and promoters.",
